If you use `@JsonBackReference` on your getter/setter method in your project more than once, you should distinguish them with a specific Reference name.

In `Role` entity class, you have used `@JsonBackReference` twice:

```lang-java
@OneToMany(mappedBy = &quot;roleName&quot;, fetch = FetchType.LAZY,cascade = CascadeType.REMOVE)
